name: Galloping Horse YouTube Progress Bar
description:
White galloping horse for YouTube progress bar! 

Watch your horse race from grassy meadows to the mysteriousness of space as you progress through any YouTube video. 

Please see description if you will be using "YouTube - Custom colors video progress bar" concurrently with this style.
